241
00:19:44,750 --> 00:19:47,350
Kobayashi Nobuo,

242
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:48,990
Mr. Haruki at Beiping,

243
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:51,670
and Lieutenant Shibayama at Nanjing.

244
